gomodel:SYNGO_4652  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Figure 9u-x. immunogold labeling in mouse cerebellum;\n\"ROCK2 IR was observed at synapses in the cerebellar molecular layer (Fig. 9U-X; U, black arrows, near active zone; V, at presynapse only; W, at both pre- and postsynapse; X, at postsynapse only).\"\n\n\"ROCK2 has been shown to localize at actin clustered at postsynaptic density (PSD) (Fig. 9W and X)\". Experimental description: \"Normal adult mice (8-week-old C57BL/6 mice) were obtained from SLC (Japan SLC, Hamamatsu, Japan).\"\n\nantibody; anti-ROCK2 antibody (1:400 dilution) (Katoh et al., 2001) PMID:11331307" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-4973-5732" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2286-1587" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2514-0216" ;
        dc:date           "2022-05-09" ;
        dc:title          "SYNGO_CC_4652" ;
        pav:providedBy    "https://syngo.vu.nl" ;
        biolink:in_taxon  "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/NCBITaxon_10090" .

